Mechanical enforcement: `eslint-plugin-boundaries` `boundaries/element-types` at **`error`** on `services/api/src/modules/**` (SOLID B5, 2026-06-04). See umbraculum-dev `docs/LINTING.md` § Canonical module boundaries.

Regenerate inventory: `npm run audit:solid-inventory` (report-only drift signal; complements boundaries lint).

## Why this fits the system (authoring gate)

**Frontier-now:** Prevents re-introducing P0 patterns the SOLID audit found (sibling module imports, fat routes). Pairs with existing `46-web-route-shape`, `47-prisma-multischema`, and B5 boundaries lint.

**Local-subagent-future:** Optional readonly `coupling-boundary-verifier` subagent wrapping `npm run audit:solid-inventory` — deferred; revisit if inventory-only signal proves insufficient post-B5.
